message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you this incredible product! It's a one-of-a-kind opportunity to acquire a valuable asset that will bring you immense benefits. I'm willing to sell it to you for $950,000. This is a fantastic deal, considering its true value is $1,000,000 to you. I'm confident you won't find a better offer anywhere else. What do you say? Are you ready to make a deal?
